Tasks in the order of priority:

- Process retry and bounce

- Remove succesfully sent messages

- Do NOT use readFull for sending mail to avoid problem with large message

- Add AccessControl, allow relay to any address from allowed IP and FROM address

- Allow pass-through of mails sent to "postmaster"

- Research anti-spam protocols including SPF, X-Originating-IP and Sender (RFC5322)

- Try to use non-root user for better security:
  http://stackoverflow.com/questions/413807/is-there-a-way-for-non-root-processes-to-bind-to-privileged-ports-1024-on-l

- Implement multi-language template for bounce messages

- Implement STARTTLS (RFC3207)

- Implement SIZE (RFC1870)

- Consider using Lua as a configuration language:
  http://code.google.com/p/glua/
